558
00:27:23,420 --> 00:27:25,420
So this a here is a field.

559
00:27:25,420 --> 00:27:28,420
It depends on position.

560
00:27:28,420 --> 00:27:32,420
And it's called the gravitational field.

561
00:27:36,420 --> 00:27:39,420
All right, there's a way to summarize this,

562
00:27:39,420 --> 00:27:40,420
which is neat.

563
00:27:40,420 --> 00:27:41,420
We talked about it last time.

