00:28:46,420 --> 00:28:49,420
is called the divergence of the field.

589
00:28:49,420 --> 00:28:54,420
The divergence of the acceleration field here

590
00:28:54,420 --> 00:28:57,420
is due to masses

591
00:28:57,420 --> 00:29:00,420
and it's proportional to the mass.

592
00:29:00,420 --> 00:29:02,420
At every point there's a divergence

593
00:29:02,420 --> 00:29:05,420
which is proportional to the amount of mass

594
00:29:05,420 --> 00:29:07,420
at that point.

595
00:29:07,420 --> 00:29:09,420
To express it mathematically,

596
00:29:09,420 --> 00:29:12,420
we have to invent a concept called mass density.

597
00:29:12,420 --> 00:29:14,420
Now we all know what we mean by mass density.

