00:29:21,420 --> 00:29:22,420
ask how much mass.

602
00:29:22,420 --> 00:29:24,420
We're now imagining that

603
00:29:24,420 --> 00:29:28,420
either that the mass is continuously distributed,

604
00:29:28,420 --> 00:29:31,420
not in the form of point particles,

605
00:29:31,420 --> 00:29:33,420
or that there are so many point particles,

606
00:29:33,420 --> 00:29:35,420
tiny, tiny point particles,

607
00:29:35,420 --> 00:29:37,420
that we might as well effectively think of it

608
00:29:37,420 --> 00:29:39,420
as being distributed.

609
00:29:39,420 --> 00:29:42,420
Then the amount of mass in a unit volume,

610
00:29:42,420 --> 00:29:45,420
or the amount of mass per unit volume,

