00:30:55,420 --> 00:30:58,420
I'll remind you where the 4 pi comes from,

635
00:30:58,420 --> 00:30:59,420
why it's there,

636
00:30:59,420 --> 00:31:01,420
times the mass density,

637
00:31:01,420 --> 00:31:05,420
oops, times Newton's constant.

638
00:31:05,420 --> 00:31:09,420
The strength of gravity is always proportional to Newton's constant,

639
00:31:09,420 --> 00:31:11,420
so the effect of a mass

