00:31:11,420 --> 00:31:14,420
is always proportional to Newton's constant.

641
00:31:14,420 --> 00:31:16,420
It's proportional to the amount of mass,

642
00:31:16,420 --> 00:31:18,420
that's the row,

643
00:31:18,420 --> 00:31:23,420
and this is the basic equation

644
00:31:23,420 --> 00:31:26,420
that you can think of as a field equation.

