00:32:38,420 --> 00:32:41,420
which also has to do with divergences of vectors.

669
00:32:41,420 --> 00:32:45,420
So let me remind you about Gauss's theorem.

670
00:32:45,420 --> 00:32:49,420
It is so central to everything in,

