00:32:54,420 --> 00:32:56,420
or 10 minutes on it.

674
00:32:56,420 --> 00:32:59,420
Gauss's theorem says

675
00:32:59,420 --> 00:33:03,420
that if you have a field

676
00:33:03,420 --> 00:33:06,420
which has a divergence,

677
00:33:06,420 --> 00:33:09,420
that divergence is a scalar,

