00:33:54,420 --> 00:33:56,420
three-dimensional cubes.

697
00:33:56,420 --> 00:33:59,420
You break it up into tiny three-dimensional cubes.

698
00:33:59,420 --> 00:34:03,420
In each cube, you take the divergence of A,

