00:34:06,420 --> 00:34:08,420
and you add them all up.

701
00:34:08,420 --> 00:34:10,420
That's integrating the divergence of A

702
00:34:10,420 --> 00:34:13,420
over the interior region here.

703
00:34:13,420 --> 00:34:17,420
What it says, or what Gauss's theorem says,

704
00:34:17,420 --> 00:34:21,420
is that that integral is equal to a surface integral,

705
00:34:21,420 --> 00:34:23,420
a sum over the surface.

